<HEADLINE>
<P>
A&E TO AIR PROFILE OF SKATER BROWNING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A&E has acquired the Canadian production "Kurt Browning: Life on the Edge" 
from Great Northern Releasing Inc. and will nationally premiere the profile of 
the Canadian figure skater on March 10 at 6 and 10 p.m. on "A&E Stage." 
</P>
<P>
 Browning won the 1993 World Figure Skating Championship, and is expected to be 
a strong contender this year in Lillehammer. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020494-0036 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 010244 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 4, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
