<DOCNO> LA020494-0043 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 010251 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 4, 1994, Friday, Valley Edition 
</P>
