<TEXT>
<P>
 Oxnard police have arrested two men on suspicion of stealing a 14-year-old 
boy's bike after forcing him to abandon it as he rode down the street, 
authorities said Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
 Homero Barajas and Gilbert Amar, both 19, were taken into custody on suspicion 
of strong-arm robbery a short time after the incident when patrol officers 
recognized their car from a description broadcast by police dispatchers.The 
bike was recovered. 
</P>
<P>
