$20,000 bail. They are scheduled to appear in Ventura County Municipal Court 
today. 
</P>
<P>
 The incident occurred about 5:50 p.m. Wednesday as the boy was riding in the 
area of Wooley and Ventura roads, police said. The boy told police a car pulled 
up beside him and the passenger got out and tried to hit him. When the boy 
abandoned his bike, the passenger threw it in the back of the car and the 
driver drove away. JULIE FIELDS 
