at Alabama, Artist Coach Mike Soylular said. 
</P>
<P>
 Kyle, an outside hitter, was the Pacific Coast League most valuable player and 
was selected first-team All-Southern Section Division I. She was first-team 
Division I and first-team All-State the previous season. 
