<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 4, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 9; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
