<HEADLINE>
<P>
VIETNAM: THE LAND AND ITS PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 From a Communist government to multimillion-dollar trade agreements, a look at 
how Vietnam compares to the United States and California: How Vietnam Compares 
04,24,15,16,16 Vietnam U.S. California Population 71 million 258 million 30 
million Life expectancy 63 years 76 years 76 years Infant mortality rate 
